data.description: Great opportunity to make this 4 bedroom home on almost an acre in award winning Lindale school district your next home! The charming entrance opens up to the living room with a cozy fireplace for the cooler months. The kitchen and breakfast area are also open to the living room, creating a  feeling of spaciousness. The kitchen features granite countertops, plenty of storage and stainless steel appliances. The refrigerator is included with this sale of this home. The main bedroom is adjacent to the kitchen with a beautiful en suite bathroom and large closet. On the opposite side of the home are three bedrooms and 1.5 baths. The half bath is open to the hallway so it’s perfect for guests! A cute mud bench greets you from the garage and the lucky new owner will get the washer and dryer included with this sale! The covered porch is overlooking the huge backyard and the pool. Imagine yourself in this peaceful country setting and make it your next home!
